---
title: Plant-Based Chick'n Tenders & Cheesy Spiced Wedges with Burger Sauce & Avocado Salad
description: A plant-based version of chick'n tenders, yes it can be done. A side of golden wedges to dip in a burger sauce (it’s great for the chick'n tenders too!) will make your mouth water in no time.

